thread.title_full: Totally Wicked E-liquid USA inc. reviewed by Triana

author: Triana
title: Triana
text:
I had heard some scary things about shopping the Vape shops on the web. Atomizers that didn't fit right being the main one that impacted me. I had dropped my eLeaf and destroyed the entire atomizer.
Although the one ordered from Totally Wicked was twice the cost of other websites, the website was pulled together and functioning for the most part. I was going to order some e-liquid too but that was challenging on the site.
All said and done, I received my atomizer in three or four days and it fit perfectly. I am very happy and would use the site again.
